data.description: This beautiful 3bd 2ba over 2,000 sq ft, is located in a quiet cul-de-sac in a great neighborhood, and is close to Wal-Mart, the Fair grounds, restaurants, Navy Federal, hospitals, and I10.  This home is the best of both worlds as it mixes a traditional and modern floor plan. As you enter the home you have a office/formal living room to the right and a dining room/library to the left. The home then opens up to a modern open floor plan that features high vaulted ceilings, board and batten accent walls, a large kitchen island that flows into the great room, granite counter tops in the kitchen, beautiful maple cabinets, updated light fixtures through out and tile backsplash. In the Great Room there are surround sound speakers already wired and mounted, barn doors, accent walls, and a custom floor plan give this home character, and style. The master bedroom is spacious and features a deep walk in closet. The master bathroom has a separate shower and tub. A single vanity with a makeup area. The additional bedrooms are spacious, and share a hallway bathroom. There is a screened in patio to enjoy the views of the backyard. There are two sheds in the backyard that can be repurposed for a perfect mancave and she shed with a fire pit out back!!
